Installation Instructions
-------------------------


Dependencies
-----------------------

qt4-dev (must have qt version 4.4 or greater)
libsqlite3-dev
cmake-2.4 (this is the build system used)
libginac-1.3.7
gsl-1.9
boost C++ libraries (only use shared_ptr.hpp)


Build and run instructions
----------------------------

1. run cmake
2. run make
3. execute ark3d


Example build and run process
------------------------------------

cmake .
make
./src/Interface/ark3d



